{"tid":1962313,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[自由度高]Crossout 創世戰車，有冇巴打仲有玩?","createTime":"2020-04-07T11:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:39:24.000Z","uid":215066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a5dd93077f9b16619d8f3cd7daabdb386d5a1046","tid":1962313,"uid":215066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"《創世戰車》由俄羅斯 Gaijin Entertainment 和 Targem games 研發的車輛組裝對戰題材線上遊戲，以廢土世界為故事背景，透過創造、操控、破壞三大特色並搭配陣營變化、鋼鐵巨獸、個性玩法、自由市場等，讓玩家能盡情享受陸上大戰。<br />\n<br />\n  在遊戲中玩家可以利用不同的配件進行組裝，將可創造出數以千計、獨一無二的造型車輛，不論是火力至上的重裝坦克車輛、速度優化的衝鋒飛車，還是造型奇特的各類車輛，都有機會在遊戲中實現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/02cvp1miRc0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F02cvp1miRc0&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=16e0a74a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/02cvp1miRc0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我見之前有人都開咗個post,  想睇下仲有冇人有玩 以下係小弟嘅車</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kmCNAr8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkmCNAr8.png&h=98df2ace&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjhFa0P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjhFa0P.png&h=c6bc8c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTm6Q04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTm6Q04.png&h=5729c1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4Ow18L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4Ow18L.png&h=fc88bba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LW28OQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LW28OQ.png&h=4cfd7208&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}